               <p>I live at <placeName id="t17830910-112-crimeloc590">Pancras</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17830910-112-crimeloc590" type="placeName" value="Pancras"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17830910-112-crimeloc590" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830910-112-off588 t17830910-112-crimeloc590"></join>, I lost in August last three cocks and eight hens, five of them were killed by the prisoner, I kept them in<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178309100144"></xptr> a house in the back-yard, I know they were my property.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17830910-112-person1174">
                  WILLIAM
                   CARDINGTON
               <interp inst="t17830910-112-person1174" type="surname" value="CARDINGTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830910-112-person1174" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830910-112-person1174" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw these fowls the day before the robbery about three or four in the afternoon, there were eleven of them, and I saw them in the morning going to Battle-bridge, they were my master's property.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>

               <p>I am lately come from the West Indies, and have had a disorder on me, I have been to several doctors, and they advised me to get snails and put them among new milk and drink a pint of it, by which I have found benefit, and I was down at Pancras, and there is a bit of a wooden bridge, and there lay a bag, I did not open it, I put it under my arm, and this man came up and asked me what I had; I am innocent.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17830910-112-verdict591" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830910-112-verdict591" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>To be <rs id="t17830910-112-punish592" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830910-112-punish592" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
